                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040215-25-defend253 t18040215-25-punish139"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Le Blanc.</p>
